---
title: Gyro Style Beef Kofta Tacos with Chips and Roasted Garlic Slaw
description: Whether you're catching the game at home or pitch-side, enjoy these Gyro Style Beef Kofta Tacos in your celebrations of the Euro championship. Perfect for fuelling your matchday fever or scoring a goal with guests.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W28_UK_F17285-2_Main_low-ba11390d.jpg
